{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act30side", "eventName": "銀心湖列車", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "RS-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "逃票？", "storyInfo": "雪山上，烈夏質疑“灰禮帽”接近自己的意圖，卻反而點醒“灰禮帽”。僵持之際，阿克托斯趕到，與烈夏一同摔下山崖。鐧隨後趕到，堵住了“灰禮帽”。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉住我的手。", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喝——哈！", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好！", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前在列車上有過一面之緣，沒想到在這裡還會被您所救。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了您伸出援手，否則我不知還要在這裡被困多久。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很感謝，羅莎琳·塔季揚諾夫娜·拉里娜小姐，感謝您的無私幫助。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……唔，小事，不用謝。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看起來肯定不是當地人，上山應該也是來旅遊的？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正是。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你怎麼不沿著大路走，跑到這種林子裡來不說，還掉進人家打獵挖的陷阱裡？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萬一我沒正好路過，你打算怎麼辦？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是被山間的景色吸引，沒有想到積雪之下會有這樣的陷阱。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒有您路過解救……那我正好可以多待一會。冷靜一下，再想辦法自己爬出去。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過現在看來，我還是幸運的。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#7$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅莎琳小姐，您是要繼續上山嗎？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？對，沒錯。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您不介意，我們可以同行一段。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也想要欣賞一番謝拉格雪山上頂的風光。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好啊。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不介意，那我們走吧。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離山頂還有好一段路程呢。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛那是……", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "萊利老爹！", "name": "謝拉格青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我檢查過了，我們佈置在這附近的陷阱被踩塌了一個，應該是有獵物掉進去過！", "name": "謝拉格青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我看的時候裡面什麼也沒有，估計是又逃了。", "name": "謝拉格青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看到剛剛過去的那人沒有？你看他，像不像圖里爾那老小子說要找的那人？", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說，是鐧小姐拜託我們找的那個……", "name": "謝拉格青年"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_277_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿得烏漆嘛黑、裝模作樣的，戴著帽子還遮著臉，錯不了！", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走！我們回去，趕快把這事告訴鐧小姐！", "name": "謝拉格老人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_279_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，那個誰……對了，我還不知道你叫什麼名字。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們不是都講究什麼，見面要先互相告知姓名嗎？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我疏忽了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鄙人名叫約翰‧史密斯，隨便您怎麼稱呼都可以。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約翰……？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這名字……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名字如何？", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這名字……聽起來和之前博士看的什麼間諜電影的主角一樣！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，我沒記錯，就是這個名字！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得主人公還有個大美女搭檔，約翰你……算了，看你能一個人來這種情侶景點，就知道你一定沒對象。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是個有趣的巧合。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對吧！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了約翰，言歸正傳，我們估計還要爬一會才能到山頂。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我聽人說過，雪山越往上就越冷，而且還會讓人越來越喘不上氣。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，你累不累？要不要休息一下？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請不必擔心我。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅莎琳小姐需要休息一下嗎？", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就不用了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來你的體力不錯，“間諜先生”。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哈哈。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來，他確實被你騙到了。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#2$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我並沒有編造謊言，鐧。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“灰禮帽”是為公爵蒐集情報的密探，一般的謊言瞞不過他們。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我深知，這種人往往最懂得“猜忌”。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“佩爾羅契家的繼承人秘密歸國”，這是他自己最先發現的事實，所以他一定會相信。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對方一定會盯上羅莎琳·塔季揚諾夫娜·拉里娜。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你總能猜對。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那女孩已經上山，菈塔托絲也聯絡了阿克托斯。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#7$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我接到消息，那個“灰禮帽“也跟上去了。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他在躲著我。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無妨。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確認他將注意力放在那女孩身上就夠了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也該出發了。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，就當飯後運動。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#2$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你確定放任“灰禮帽”接近那個女孩，之後那個博士不會找你麻煩？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「灰禮帽」是間諜，不是殺手，他要的是情報，而不是性命。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算這麼向那個博士解釋？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#2$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士那邊我會向他——道歉。", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確實該道歉。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#1$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我如何不重要，相較之下，我更好奇——", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鐧，你也記得博士了？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Sharp作為對手來說還不錯，比大部分草包騎士強得多。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能被那樣的戰士推崇，又能讓你吃點虧，這人記一記也無妨。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#9$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#9$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_172_svrash_1#4$1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.0, "offsetx": 350.0, "width": 300.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你對博士很好奇？", "name": "恩希歐迪斯"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以這麼說。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，閒話就到這裡。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我該辦正事了。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g12_mountpath", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呀吼——！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "終於到了——！！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，一共爬了有幾個小時了吧？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "累死我了，怪不得大家都選擇留在山腰，這也太累人了。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的風景確實不錯……那邊那個是不是銀心湖？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，從這看耶拉岡德像還沒我拇指大！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#5$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "冬季的銀心湖會冰封，從這裡看下去，就像是一塊色彩澄淨的寶石一般。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因此，謝拉格當地人都認為銀心湖是耶拉岡德賜下的瑰寶。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實是只有站得夠高才能看到的風景。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實還挺像寶石的。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，那邊還能看到車站！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼看謝拉格的鐵路也不少了嘛，就是列車看起來像玩具一樣……", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於一個正在發展的國家來說，這樣的鐵道數量並不算多。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會看起來數量眾多，只是因為這裡是銀心湖，還有耶拉岡德像在此。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然目前還不比聖山，但已經修建通車的鐵道線路，都會途經這裡，在此中轉……", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……目前的路線都會在銀心湖中轉……？", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別發呆了，約翰，幫我個忙。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能幫我在這附近找找有沒有長在一起的兩棵樹嗎？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "應該是老樹，枝幹的部分纏在一起，形狀看起來很奇怪的兩棵樹！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#8$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂意效勞。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝了！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，約翰。", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你都不問問我找樹是要幹嘛？", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不是也沒問過我，我上山是要幹嘛？", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我琢磨了一下……還是決定用我更擅長的辦法解決問題。", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老實點別亂動！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cnstrctnck"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……羅莎琳小姐，您這是什麼意思？", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別這副口吻，我還沒把你怎麼樣呢。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說吧，你暗中跟了我這麼久，到山頂也沒個動作，到底想幹什麼？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不明白您的意思。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少裝傻。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不記得有告訴過你我的名字。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是個誤會。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您知道，我和哈洛德·克雷加文子爵閣下有舊，是他向我透露了羅莎琳小姐的姓名。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#6$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clnchfst"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不是覺得我很好騙？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我根本就沒告訴那個大叔我的全名，他怎麼可能告訴你？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且你這傢伙能一口氣爬上山頂，連喘都不喘兩聲，根本不可能掉進普通獵人挖的陷阱！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算掉進去，也不至於上不來。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安娜她們總是要我多想想再行動，但要我說，有時候想太多反而沒用。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您比我想的要細心許多，羅莎琳小姐。", "name": "“約翰·史密斯”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這是承認了？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "約翰·史密斯這個名字多半也是假的吧？難道說……你真是間諜？", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我說我是呢？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你這行一定做得不怎麼樣。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#9$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連我都看得出來不對勁。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#13$1"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的指摘完全正確。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，我確實有許多大意之處，在謝拉格的生活讓我有些疏於遮掩。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟在謝拉格境內的行動還算自由，並且能夠對我有所威脅的人，實在不多。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈，口氣不小。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我警告你，老實點，別想亂動。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你現在可是在山崖邊，腳下只有積雪。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要我跺跺腳，這裡的雪就會崩落，到時候我可不敢保證一定會拉住你。", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#4$1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，羅莎琳小姐，那我也直說好了，你昨天……", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的小子！！", "name": "阿克托斯"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿克托斯在此！你給我離她遠點！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_194_leto_1#14$1"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！你、你從哪冒出來的啊大叔！", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#14$1"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊啊等下！你別跺腳，等下——", "name": "烈夏"}, "figure_art": "avg_194_leto_1#14$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbodyfall"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-20", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇啊啊——！", "name": "烈夏"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅、羅莎琳！", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#5$1"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓住我——", "name": "阿克托斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_254_1#8$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然有些滑稽，但阿克托斯顯然是衝著我來的——", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道說，羅莎琳真的是帶著目的來到這座山上的？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，來都來了，只能跳了。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_twohandedblunt", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……黑騎士。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "休息好了嗎？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還沒。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不太好。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "打起來少點意思。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼直接？", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "直接不好嗎？", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#6$1"}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我也直接一點吧。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓哈洛德子爵相信，列車上的一切都是誤會，當時我也只是半信半疑。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而現在，我知道了，原來堂堂黑騎士也會騙人。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那表示你對我的了解還遠遠不夠。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在轉身下山，還能好好吃一頓午飯。", "name": "鐧"}, "figure_art": "avg_4116_blkkgt_1#11$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，我一旦投入工作，就會廢寢忘食。", "name": "“灰禮帽”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_867_1#1$1"}, {"id": 367, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}